description: Enjoy Luxury living at 22 Liberty Drive Premier waterfront residences.This Spectacular 9th floor,1 bedroom plus den residence features a gorgeous kitchen,centers around the beautiful large waterfall island with custom high-gloss white lacquer cabinetry,quartz countertop state of the art-appliances Wolf stove&wall oven,Subzero,Miele,wine chiller.Spacious open floor plan over looking the living/dining room with floor to ceiling windows,custom built-ins.Pivate balcony over looking the beautiful Seaport District with partial water views.Primary bedroom suite which boasts a luxurious bathroom w/marble soaking tub,glass enclosed shower,double vanity,custom walk-in-closet.The Den features murphy bed w/double bunk beds that can be a great home office.Storage unit,1 garage parking.Amenities include 24 hour concierge/doorman,fitness center,residents lounge,private waterfront terrace over looking the harbor walk.Enjoy Seaport District finest restaurants,cafes.shops & just minutes to the Airport.
